Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.82,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Just a hero
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:15.04,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}How do I live? How do I dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.88,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Sometimes wanna sing the blues
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:22.96,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Must tighten my reins, but hard to obey
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:25.97,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}You know, I’m not perfect enough
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:29.35,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}How do I grieve? How do I scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.97,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}I just wanna be that guy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:37.35,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Yes, I’m still overwhelmed but no time to rest
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:43.36,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}And I will say here I come
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:51.64,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}我只是另一个英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:14:01.19,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}你没听到那求救的呼唤声吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.82,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}你是英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:15.04,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}该如何生存？该如何实现梦想？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.88,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}有时我也会垂头丧气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:22.96,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}必须控制好感情，但很难遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:25.97,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}你知道的，我还不够完美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:29.35,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}我该伤心吗？我该尖叫吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.97,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}但是我想成为“那个人”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:37.35,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}是的，我依旧难以承受这些，但我没有时间停下步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:43.36,BGM,,0,0,0,,{\an9}我会说：“我，来了！”
